reviews.review_text:
local boy when my buddy Robbie Branch (now long gone RIP) told me the Dead were gonna play the Fairgrounds, i was stunned that they'd come to my hometown. and what a weekend it was !
thanks to all involved for this excellent recording under difficult circumstances. it was windy.
